                <h3 class="card-title">Mill Springs Battlefield National Monument</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>The Union won a significant victory early in the Civil War at The Battle of Mill Springs. Explore the rolling fields of Kentucky where the battle took place and learn about that state's strategic importance to both sides of the fight.</p>
                <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
